---
title: Mushroom Ravioli in Garlic Cream Sauce with Green Peas and Crispy Shallots
description: Savoury mushroom ravioli is smothered in a creamy garlic and mushroom sauce, packed full of aromatics blend and green peas. Finished off with crispy shallots and fresh parsley, this dish is pure comfort in a bowl.
